God, I thank you for all

00:29:05.360 --> 00:29:06.950
the people that are representing you.

00:29:08.559 --> 00:29:11.590
We have the

00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:13.830
best of the best prayer warriors on this

00:29:13.840 --> 00:29:16.149
prayer channel.

00:29:16.159 --> 00:29:19.350
Every

00:29:19.360 --> 00:29:22.549
single person brings their supply

00:29:24.159 --> 00:29:25.830
because when we pray

00:29:25.840 --> 00:29:28.710
together, there's power, for

00:29:28.720 --> 00:29:31.110
Many hands make light work.

00:29:34.960 --> 00:29:36.710
Father, I thank you for every

00:29:36.720 --> 00:29:38.230
single person represented here

00:29:38.240 --> 00:29:39.990
tonight. I call them healed and whole

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:42.070
and well.

00:29:42.080 --> 00:29:44.070
My wife and I, and my son, we all

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:45.909
agree that they are healed and

00:29:45.919 --> 00:29:47.430
whole and well, and they lack no good

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:49.430
thing.

00:29:55.840 --> 00:29:59.029
We lift up this body before

00:29:59.039 --> 00:30:01.269
you.

00:30:01.279 --> 00:30:02.950
We thank you, Lord, that you were

00:30:02.960 --> 00:30:05.110
wounded for our transgressions

00:30:05.110 --> 00:30:05.120
and

00:30:05.120 --> 00:30:06.149
bruised for our iniquity. The

00:30:06.159 --> 00:30:08.310
chastisement of our peace was upon you,

00:30:08.320 --> 00:30:10.149
and with your stripes, we are

00:30:10.159 --> 00:30:11.909
healed.

00:30:11.909 --> 00:30:11.919
This

00:30:11.919 --> 00:30:14.230
represents

00:30:14.240 --> 00:30:16.950
so much more than just a little

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:19.590
wafer in a cup of juice.

00:30:19.600 --> 00:30:21.990
Jesus paid the price for us to walk in

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:24.470
victory over sickness, disease,

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:27.990
poverty, lack, and mental torment.

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.669
People are battling depression during

00:30:29.679 --> 00:30:31.350
this holiday season.

00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:33.990
They feel alone or

00:30:33.990 --> 00:30:34.000
that

00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:36.070
they

00:30:36.080 --> 00:30:37.590
don't have relatives.

00:30:39.520 --> 00:30:41.590
But

00:30:41.600 --> 00:30:43.350
Father, you said you'd never leave us

00:30:43.360 --> 00:30:46.470
and you'd never forsake us.

00:30:50.240 --> 00:30:52.549
You're their family during this

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:55.110
beautiful holiday season. We

00:30:55.120 --> 00:30:58.470
lift up the people who are alone and we

00:30:58.480 --> 00:31:00.789
thank you, Father, that they are never

00:31:00.799 --> 00:31:03.750
alone because you're always with them. I

00:31:03.760 --> 00:31:06.149
pray, Father, for peace. You are the

00:31:06.159 --> 00:31:08.789
Prince of Peace. And Father, right now,

00:31:08.799 --> 00:31:11.750
I ask you to flood their hearts, flood

00:31:11.760 --> 00:31:13.750
their minds, flood their beings,

00:31:13.760 --> 00:31:15.510
Father, with your holy, beautiful

00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:19.350
presence. That

00:31:19.350 --> 00:31:19.360
sweet-smelling

00:31:19.360 --> 00:31:21.990
fragrance, the fragrance of the Holy

00:31:22.000 --> 00:31:24.070
Spirit, that peace that passes

00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:25.830
all understanding. Goodness and mercy

00:31:25.840 --> 00:31:27.190
will follow them all the days of their

00:31:27.200 --> 00:31:28.950
life. Father, if they've lost somebody

00:31:28.960 --> 00:31:31.750
tragically this year,

00:31:31.760 --> 00:31:34.630
like Erica—she lost Charlie and

00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:36.470
their kids are in this first

00:31:36.480 --> 00:31:38.630
Thanksgiving without having their

00:31:38.640 --> 00:31:41.509
father there, without having her husband

00:31:41.509 --> 00:31:41.519
there—and

00:31:41.519 --> 00:31:43.830
anybody else who lost

00:31:43.840 --> 00:31:45.909
somebody that's dear to them this year,

00:31:45.919 --> 00:31:47.750
I thank you, Father, that you fill that

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:49.669
void.

00:31:49.679 --> 00:31:52.870
Father, that you are that joy; we

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:55.669
find that joy unspeakable and full of

00:31:55.679 --> 00:31:58.789
glory in these last days. Father, I know

00:31:58.799 --> 00:32:01.909
that days of darkness and days of hardness

00:32:01.919 --> 00:32:04.070
come, but Father, you said, 'Occupy until

00:32:04.080 --> 00:32:05.909
I come and enjoy life.'Brandon, you tell

00:32:05.919 --> 00:32:07.350
me all the time, 'Brandon, just enjoy

00:32:07.360 --> 00:32:10.149
life. I want you to have fun and enjoy

00:32:10.159 --> 00:32:12.870
life. Don't look at all the darkness

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:15.190
around you. Keep vertical and keep your

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:17.430
eyes on me in this darkness.'And dark

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:20.389
times will come; dark times happen. But

00:32:20.399 --> 00:32:23.110
Father, you are my vertical.

00:32:23.120 --> 00:32:26.630
We keep our eyes on you and we don't go

00:32:26.640 --> 00:32:28.789
horizontal looking all around us. We

00:32:28.799 --> 00:32:32.070
keep our eyes on you. We stay the course

00:32:32.080 --> 00:32:35.350
knowing that you are that peace.

00:32:35.360 --> 00:32:37.830
I pray for every single person right now

00:32:37.840 --> 00:32:40.950
that has that sense of just that void of

00:32:40.960 --> 00:32:44.389
depression and anxiety and feeling

00:32:44.399 --> 00:32:47.190
so lonely. We thank you, Lord, that you

00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:50.310
are that God who brings comfort

00:32:50.320 --> 00:32:53.909
to the person who needs comfort.

00:32:53.919 --> 00:32:55.830
I believe, Father, that this is the day

00:32:55.840 --> 00:32:57.190
that they're going to have a turnaround

00:32:57.200 --> 00:33:00.070
in their emotions, a turnaround in the

00:33:00.080 --> 00:33:02.870
sadness that they feel. And Father,

00:33:02.880 --> 00:33:04.630
those who are full of joy right

00:33:04.640 --> 00:33:06.549
now and this is a breeze for

00:33:06.549 --> 00:33:06.559
them—they

00:33:06.559 --> 00:33:08.470
love the holidays; the holidays are

00:33:08.480 --> 00:33:11.029
awesome; they love this time of

00:33:11.029 --> 00:33:11.039
year—I

00:33:11.039 --> 00:33:12.710
thank you that you would double the joy

00:33:12.720 --> 00:33:14.630
on their lives and that, Father, it

00:33:14.640 --> 00:33:16.710
would flow out of them and

00:33:16.720 --> 00:33:18.950
spill over to the people who are

00:33:18.960 --> 00:33:21.750
not having that joyous time.

00:33:21.760 --> 00:33:23.750
Father, you brought joy on

00:33:23.760 --> 00:33:25.990
every single one of us, that joy

00:33:26.000 --> 00:33:29.029
unspeakable and full of glory. Father,

00:33:29.039 --> 00:33:30.950
we don't just harbor it in

00:33:30.950 --> 00:33:30.960
ourselves,

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:32.470
but we dump it out on the other people

00:33:32.480 --> 00:33:35.110
and they see that light and they say,

00:33:35.120 --> 00:33:37.990
'There's hope in your eyes.

00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:41.269
There's joy in your

00:33:41.269 --> 00:33:41.279
eyes.'And

00:33:41.279 --> 00:33:43.110
every single one of us would be

00:33:43.120 --> 00:33:44.950
that salt and we wouldn't lose our

00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:47.430
saltiness.

00:33:47.440 --> 00:33:49.509
I thank you, Father, for this beautiful

00:33:49.519 --> 00:33:52.870
Thanksgiving season that's coming up.

00:33:52.880 --> 00:33:55.110
There's peace in homes and there's no

00:33:55.120 --> 00:33:57.669
strife around the tables when we

00:33:57.679 --> 00:33:59.669
eat as families in the days ahead; that

00:33:59.679 --> 00:34:01.430
you're not bickering and fighting.

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:03.909
Father, there's peace, and there's not

00:34:03.919 --> 00:34:07.269
Democrat versus Republican and Catholic

00:34:07.279 --> 00:34:10.149
against the charismatic; we all get

00:34:10.159 --> 00:34:14.389
along and they say, 'Man, there's just joy.

00:34:14.399 --> 00:34:15.829
I love being around

00:34:15.829 --> 00:34:15.839
you.'I

00:34:15.839 --> 00:34:17.190
have to

00:34:17.200 --> 00:34:18.389
tell myself all the time because I was

00:34:18.399 --> 00:34:19.829
not a person who liked Christmas

00:34:19.839 --> 00:34:23.270
for years; in fact, I despised Christmas.

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:25.270
Not because of Jesus, but because of being around

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:27.510
people. And I had to say it to myself, 'I

00:34:27.520 --> 00:34:30.710
love Christmas. I love being around

00:34:30.710 --> 00:34:30.720
folks.'I

00:34:30.720 --> 00:34:32.710
say it all the time;

00:34:32.720 --> 00:34:33.909
I have to say it to myself all the time.

00:34:33.919 --> 00:34:35.990
I'm just being real with y'all.

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:37.589
It's something that I've struggled with

00:34:37.599 --> 00:34:39.030
all the time. I used to go around even

00:34:39.040 --> 00:34:40.950
whenever I was saying, 'I hate the Christmas

00:34:40.960 --> 00:34:42.470
season.'And

00:34:42.480 --> 00:34:44.310
that may sound really bad, but I'm

00:34:44.320 --> 00:34:45.430
just telling you something I've had to

00:34:45.440 --> 00:34:47.190
overcome.

00:34:47.200 --> 00:34:50.310
I say, 'I love the Christmas

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:52.629
season. I love this timeframe of the

00:34:52.639 --> 00:34:55.270
year. I love the

00:34:55.270 --> 00:34:55.280
lights.'I

00:34:55.280 --> 00:34:58.150
thank God for

00:34:58.160 --> 00:35:00.230
Christmas get-togethers at the church

00:35:00.240 --> 00:35:02.790
or whatever. I used to hate that; I

00:35:02.800 --> 00:35:04.470
used to say it so much and I had what I

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:06.630
said, and it's something that

00:35:06.640 --> 00:35:08.390
I've

00:35:08.400 --> 00:35:11.430
worked on because Diana loves Christmas.

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:14.630
Loves it. And so do my kids.

00:35:14.640 --> 00:35:16.310
But I just always go... and they said,

00:35:16.320 --> 00:35:18.310
'Daddy, why do you always say

00:35:18.310 --> 00:35:18.320
that?'I

00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:20.870
say, 'I don't know. I need to work on

00:35:20.880 --> 00:35:22.790
it.'And

00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:24.390
so I've worked on it; it's

00:35:24.400 --> 00:35:26.550
something that I love now.

00:35:26.560 --> 00:35:29.190
I go, 'Hey, I love this

00:35:29.190 --> 00:35:29.200
season.'Paisley

00:35:29.200 --> 00:35:33.190
loves it; it's so wonderful.

00:35:33.200 --> 00:35:35.910
I don't like the materialism of it. I

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:36.950
think that's where it all started with

00:35:36.960 --> 00:35:39.030
me as somebody growing

00:35:39.040 --> 00:35:42.310
up. I hate the materialistic side of it,

00:35:42.320 --> 00:35:44.470
how everybody acts.

00:35:44.480 --> 00:35:47.349
I don't like all of the spending and

00:35:47.359 --> 00:35:51.430
the debt and the pressure—'Well, you

00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:53.030
bought me this and I've got to

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:54.710
buy you that because if you don't, it's

00:35:54.720 --> 00:35:56.150
offensive because your gift is not as

00:35:56.160 --> 00:35:58.870
nice as mine.'I don't like that

00:35:58.880 --> 00:36:01.589
competitive crap and it's why I always

00:36:01.599 --> 00:36:03.430
was like, 'You know what? I don't

00:36:03.440 --> 00:36:04.710
want to participate in it.'So

00:36:04.710 --> 00:36:04.720
anyone

00:36:04.720 --> 00:36:05.670
say, 'What you want for

00:36:05.670 --> 00:36:05.680
Christmas?'Nothing.

00:36:05.680 --> 00:36:08.790
I don't want anything. And

00:36:08.800 --> 00:36:10.390
that's the way I always was for a long

00:36:10.400 --> 00:36:12.710
time. 'I'll bless you.''Don't bless me. I

00:36:12.720 --> 00:36:14.870
don't care about

00:36:14.870 --> 00:36:14.880
it.'And

00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:17.589
that's why there's a lot of

00:36:17.599 --> 00:36:19.670
people that are similar to

00:36:19.680 --> 00:36:21.910
being like that. So I'm just

00:36:21.920 --> 00:36:23.430
trying to encourage you. Christmas is

00:36:23.440 --> 00:36:25.910
beautiful. It's about Jesus.

00:36:25.920 --> 00:36:29.030
He deserves a day. People say,

00:36:29.040 --> 00:36:30.470
'Well, it's pagan. You're doing this and

00:36:30.470 --> 00:36:30.480
that.'No.

00:36:30.480 --> 00:36:34.550
Jesus deserves a day. Jesus

00:36:34.560 --> 00:36:36.470
deserves a year. Jesus deserves

00:36:36.480 --> 00:36:39.190
everything. But if you don't celebrate

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:40.630
him at Christmas, celebrate him

00:36:40.640 --> 00:36:42.150
sometime.

00:36:42.160 --> 00:36:44.550
He deserves it.

00:36:44.560 --> 00:36:46.870
That's what I told my kids. We make him a

00:36:46.870 --> 00:36:46.880
big

00:36:46.880 --> 00:36:49.589
Christmas cake and write

00:36:49.599 --> 00:36:52.310
'Happy Birthday'on it. We even

00:36:52.320 --> 00:36:54.150
allowed you all to be a part of that

00:36:54.160 --> 00:36:57.190
last year. We celebrated and had a cake

00:36:57.200 --> 00:36:59.109
and did it all. We show you what we do

00:36:59.119 --> 00:37:01.670
as a family. We make it about Jesus

00:37:01.670 --> 00:37:01.680
being

00:37:01.680 --> 00:37:04.710
the reason for the season. And all of

00:37:04.710 --> 00:37:04.720
this—all

00:37:04.720 --> 00:37:06.710
the materialism, all Black

00:37:06.720 --> 00:37:09.510
Friday, and all the hype—I keep Jesus

00:37:09.520 --> 00:37:12.390
the main thing. I

00:37:12.400 --> 00:37:15.190
refuse to rob him of it and let Santa

00:37:15.200 --> 00:37:17.750
Claus take the glory. Santa Claus

00:37:17.750 --> 00:37:17.760
isn't

00:37:17.760 --> 00:37:20.630
coming to my house.

00:37:20.630 --> 00:37:20.640
I'm

00:37:20.640 --> 00:37:22.470
always saying Santa Claus

00:37:22.470 --> 00:37:22.480
doesn't

00:37:22.480 --> 00:37:25.589
exist in this house. Jesus does.

00:37:25.599 --> 00:37:27.670
He's the provider. There isn't a man in

00:37:27.680 --> 00:37:31.510
a red suit. Jesus provides for my kids.

00:37:31.520 --> 00:37:33.670
I never let someone take the glory

00:37:33.680 --> 00:37:35.349
other than Jesus Christ; he gets all the

00:37:35.359 --> 00:37:37.430
glory in my house. And we've raised our

00:37:37.440 --> 00:37:39.910
kids that way. Jesus is the reason for

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:42.069
this season, not some big guy in a red

00:37:42.079 --> 00:37:44.310
suit. It's fun, okay, a fairy tale,

00:37:44.320 --> 00:37:46.950
whatever you want to say, but Jesus

00:37:46.950 --> 00:37:46.960
is

00:37:46.960 --> 00:37:49.430
the reason. He is the reason for our

00:37:49.440 --> 00:37:51.910
season. And we give him all the glory,

00:37:51.920 --> 00:37:53.589
honor, and praise. And we give him a

00:37:53.599 --> 00:37:55.190
birthday cake; he may not eat it

00:37:55.200 --> 00:37:56.630
in the natural, but we

00:37:56.640 --> 00:37:58.870
celebrate with him like he's there. And

00:37:58.880 --> 00:38:01.190
we have video showing

00:38:01.200 --> 00:38:04.150
you what we do.

00:38:04.160 --> 00:38:06.950
It's all glory to Jesus.

00:38:06.960 --> 00:38:09.910
We always give the glory to Jesus in

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:12.069
this beautiful season. And now we give

00:38:12.079 --> 00:38:14.470
you praise and thanksgiving.

00:38:14.470 --> 00:38:14.480
You

00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:17.270
are so real to us,

00:38:17.280 --> 00:38:19.430
and when you get real with God, God

00:38:19.440 --> 00:38:22.390
will become real to you. We make sure we

00:38:22.400 --> 00:38:24.550
always keep the main thing the main

00:38:24.560 --> 00:38:28.950
thing. Jesus is important in our home.

00:38:28.960 --> 00:38:32.310
Jesus is provider. Jesus is our healer.

00:38:32.320 --> 00:38:36.150
Jesus is our comforter.

00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:38.630
You got that there, babe?

00:38:38.640 --> 00:38:41.109
There it is.

00:38:41.119 --> 00:38:44.390
Merry Christmas.

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:46.790
Brownies or cookies or something. And so

00:38:46.800 --> 00:38:48.470
this year, Diana found

00:38:48.480 --> 00:38:49.270
it.

00:38:49.280 --> 00:38:50.470
Happy?

00:38:50.480 --> 00:38:51.430
Did you see it?

00:38:51.440 --> 00:38:53.510
Yeah.

00:38:53.520 --> 00:38:55.430
It's important.

00:38:55.440 --> 00:38:58.790
It's so important. Thank you, Father.

00:38:58.800 --> 00:39:00.470
Thank you, Father, for what you did for

00:39:00.480 --> 00:39:03.190
this household this year. As we close

00:39:03.200 --> 00:39:05.750
out 2025,

00:39:05.760 --> 00:39:08.390
thank you that we are thriving and we come

00:39:08.400 --> 00:39:10.390
alive and all the things you can say to

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:12.550
rhyme with it.

00:39:12.560 --> 00:39:14.390
Everything that was is what you've done

00:39:14.400 --> 00:39:16.470
for us and we're so grateful. We're so

00:39:16.480 --> 00:39:18.630
healed and whole and

00:39:18.630 --> 00:39:18.640
well—mentally,

00:39:18.640 --> 00:39:20.550
emotionally, physically, financially.

00:39:20.560 --> 00:39:23.750
You have been good to Brandon and Diana,

00:39:23.750 --> 00:39:23.760
and

00:39:23.760 --> 00:39:26.230
my children. We praise you, Father. We

00:39:26.240 --> 00:39:28.790
thank you, Lord, for 2025 as we have

00:39:28.800 --> 00:39:31.270
a day of thanksgiving coming. We take

00:39:31.280 --> 00:39:34.550
this body right now in

00:39:34.550 --> 00:39:34.560
Jesus'name.

00:39:34.560 --> 00:39:36.470
I know it was different, but it's just

00:39:36.480 --> 00:39:39.109
from the heart. People make things so

00:39:39.119 --> 00:39:41.109
religious.

00:39:41.119 --> 00:39:44.630
Get real with God; he will become real

00:39:44.640 --> 00:39:49.190
to you. Stop treating him like

00:39:49.200 --> 00:39:51.510
he's untouchable. He wants you to sit in

00:39:51.520 --> 00:39:53.430
his lap.

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:57.670
Jesus made it possible for you to sit

00:39:57.680 --> 00:39:59.990
with him in the heavenlies

00:40:00.000 --> 00:40:03.270
and take the blood of Jesus. What

00:40:03.280 --> 00:40:06.390
represents the blood is what makes it

00:40:06.400 --> 00:40:12.550
that way. Thank you, Jesus, for your blood,

00:40:12.560 --> 00:40:14.950
because if it wasn't for you,

00:40:14.950 --> 00:40:14.960
who

00:40:14.960 --> 00:40:16.630
eradicated sin and got rid of it

00:40:16.640 --> 00:40:20.630
all, I would be in so much trouble. We

00:40:20.630 --> 00:40:20.640
would

00:40:20.640 --> 00:40:23.030
all have to sacrifice a

00:40:23.040 --> 00:40:24.550
bull, and the vegans would really hate

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:26.630
it. What would you do then if we still had

00:40:26.640 --> 00:40:28.870
